text: Kangshubi or Kangsubi is a Meitei Manipuri ethnic food item. It is a local sweet made up of grounded seeds and other ingredients. It is a very popular food item in the Indian state of Manipur, especially among the Manipuri ethnicity. ==Other website== * https://www.recipes18.com/all/recipe/kangsubi/ ==References== Category:Meitei food
title: Kangshubi
